br />\nShe only apologised when she got exposed. We do not think her apology is sincere and an apology video is not enough.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nWe do not tolerate this kind of disgsuting, inhumane behaviour. It&rsquo;s been months but until now, the authorities haven&rsquo;t take any actions yet.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nAs a concerned citizen, we would like for you to think twice about inviting her to the Italy film event.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nThousands and millions of people are suffering depression and anxiety because of bullying. If you&rsquo;re still considering inviting her to the event after reading this, that means you guys support bullying and that means you are a part of the problem.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">(意大利電影節個Facebook )</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/64396356785/posts/10155959642056786\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F64396356785%2Fposts%2F10155959642056786&d=hmtFoPnP%2FIv5fOqUL3ZUaje9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=9ede863b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/64396356785/posts/10155959642056786</a>"},{"pid":"260fe281d195f45de03e5a10541ad531ac3eac6b","tid":1107714,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T22:58:27.000Z","msg":"唔好推啦"},{"pid":"744c0f7154db837cfca9760047cea05aee73b66e","tid":1107714,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T23:37:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78dd4a3a31dc811259904e119bb22a5a9cdfc486","tid":1107714,"uid":21536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T02:35:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833313589019646b8665cec9a70c0c57cb7520a5","tid":1107714,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T04:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa